OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FEngland faced their first weather-
OL,7,Frelated delay on Wednesday, with the
OL,8,Fside's friendly against Costa Rica
OL,9,Fdelayed by an hour due to heavy rain
OL,10,Fand thunderstorms.
OL,12,FIt was the team's first test against
OL,13,Fthe challenging climate conditions
OL,14,Fexpected across tournament, which
OL,15,Fkicks off in the US, Mexico and Canada
OL,16,Fon June 11.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
