OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781615475
OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,F"We see the adaptation to the heat, we
OL,7,Fsee the adaptation to the climate and
OL,8,Fwe see things clicking, but we
OL,9,Fdemanded from the players to take a
OL,10,Fnext step, and they did," head coach
OL,11,FThomas Tuchel said following the game.
OL,13,FWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,14,Fand are other World Cup games likely
OL,15,Fto be affected? ITV News explains.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
