OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FWhat causes thunderstorms?
OL,8,FThe two vital ingredients for a
OL,9,Fthunderstorm are instability in the
OL,10,Fatmosphere and moisture,
OL,11,Fmeteorologists say.
OL,13,FStorms take place when there is more
OL,14,Fhumid air in the system, which is
OL,15,Flikely to be the case across the US,
OL,16,FMexico, and Canada this summer, with
OL,17,Fforecasters predicting record-breaking
OL,18,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
