OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FThunder is the sound produced by the
OL,7,Frapid heating of air by a lightning
OL,8,Fstrike, and lightning is the
OL,9,Felectrical discharge that flows
OL,10,Fbetween clouds, from a cloud to air,
OL,11,For from a cloud to the ground,
OL,12,Faccording to the Met Office
OL,13,Fdescriptions.
OL,15,FBeing outdoors during a lightning
OL,16,Fstrikes is dangerous due to the
OL,17,Felectrical currents that can ripple
OL,18,Fthrough the air.
OL,20,FWhat is the World Cup protocol for
OL,21,Fthunderstorms?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
