OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FA game will be called off if lightning
OL,7,Fis detected within eight miles of a
OL,8,Fstadium during the World Cup,
OL,9,Faccording to the National Oceanic and
OL,10,FAtmospheric Administration, whose
OL,11,Frecommendations FIFA is using.
OL,13,FPlay can then only be resumed 30
OL,14,Fminutes after the last strike, meaning
OL,15,Fgames could end up being paused
OL,16,Findefinitely in a prolonged
OL,17,Fthunderstorm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
