OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FFIFA has said it will address how long
OL,7,Fmatches can be delayed on a case-by-
OL,8,Fcase basis and has not established a
OL,9,Fmaximum time until a game will
OL,10,Fautomatically be called off.
OL,12,FWhich games might be affected?
OL,14,FFlorida is the lightning capital of
OL,15,Fthe US, with June and July the peak
OL,16,Fmonths for thunderstorms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
