OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FThe Dallas, Atlanta and Houston
OL,7,Fstadiums each have roof coverage
OL,8,Favailable, which could reduce the
OL,9,Fimpact of the weather.
OL,11,FEngland could find themselves at risk
OL,12,Fof delays again when they face Ghana
OL,13,Fin Boston on June 23 and Panama in New
OL,14,FJersey on June 27.
OL,16,FHave other games been affected?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
