OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FA friendly between Saudi Arabia and
OL,7,FPuerto Rico was stopped for nearly two
OL,8,Fhours in Austin, Texas, last week
OL,9,Fafter thunderstorms forced players off
OL,10,Fthe pitch at the 21st minute.
OL,12,FMessages were displayed to fans
OL,13,Fadvising them to seek shelter under
OL,14,Fthe canopy or indoors, before the game
OL,15,Fresumed and Saudi Arabia won 3-0.
OL,17,FThe Club World Cup in 2025 also
OL,18,Fstruggled against lightning strikes,
OL,19,Fand six matches were halted due to
OL,20,Fstorms across the tournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
