OL,3,CWhat is FIFA's thunderstorm protocol
OL,4,Cand which World Cup games are at risk?
OL,6,FOne game between Chelsea and S.L.
OL,7,FBenfica finished four hours and 38
OL,8,Fminutes after it kicked off after a
OL,9,Fstorm stopped play 85 minutes in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
